      "title": "Another unidentified dead body is dumped on the shore of Galumuvadora",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A dead body of an unknown person was found on the beach of Galle mouth early this morning, Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Nihal Talduwa said.",
